query {
  ~version: 
}

docs {
  ## Get Purchase Request Template by ID
  ดึงเทมเพลตใบขอซื้อเฉพาะพร้อมรายการสินค้าและจำนวนที่กำหนดไว้ล่วงหน้า ช่วยให้ผู้ใช้ตรวจสอบหรือใช้เทมเพลตสำหรับสร้างคำขอจัดซื้อใหม่

  Retrieves a specific purchase request template with its predefined item list and quantities, allowing users to review or use the template for creating a new procurement request.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |
  | `id` | string (UUID) | Purchase Request Template ID |

  ### Query Parameters
  | Name | Type | Required | Default | Description |
  |------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
  | `version` | string | No | latest | API version |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  - **Permission key**: `procurement.purchase_request_template:view`
  - **Roles**: Requestor, HOD, Purchase, Approval

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
      "name": "Weekly Kitchen Supplies",
      "description": "Standard weekly order template for kitchen department",
      "workflow_id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4e",
      "workflow_name": "Purchase Approval Workflow",
      "is_active": true,
      "tb_purchase_request_template_detail": [
        {
          "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4f",
          "product_id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c50",
          "product_name": "Chicken Breast",
          "inventory_unit_name": "kg",
          "requested_qty": 10,
          "is_active": true
        }
      ],
      "created_at": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z",
      "updated_at": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 401 | Missing or invalid Bearer token |
  | 403 | User lacks `procurement.purchase_request_template:view` permission |
  | 404 | Template not found |

  > Service-layer errors propagate via TCP; see micro-business for full list.
}

params:path {
  id: {{pr_template_id}}
}
